nodes.text: A female individual was the fiancée of Kendal Ozzel. She had loyalties to an anti-Imperial rebel force and attempted to recruit Ozzel to her side, though he had already decided his loyalty was to the Empire. Thus, their wedding was called off, and they never saw each other again.

Ozzel went on to join the Empire, eventually rising to become an admiral in the Imperial Navy. In 3 ABY, as Ozzel was being Force choked to death by the Sith Lord Darth Vader, he thought back on his life and realized he had given everything over to authoritarians. Among the possibilities he realized he lost was the chance at a life with his fiancée.
